<item>
            <title>[PIG-398] Expressions not allowed inside foreach</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-398</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following used to work but no longer does:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A = load &apos;data&apos;;&lt;br/&gt;
B = group A by $0;&lt;br/&gt;
C = foreach B{&lt;br/&gt;
   D = MAX(A.$0)&lt;br/&gt;
   generate D;&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;</description>
